            </roles>
            <note>Added by Julia based on reflect-v.02. Corresponds to VNcls marvel-31.3-8.</note>
            <example name="both args" src="" type="">
                <inflection aspect="ns" form="ns" person="ns" tense="ns" voice="ns"/>
                <text>Mr. Lu 's reflections on 6 years as a cancer sufferer in China .</text>
